# No Proactive Cost Decisions

Never select options that incur financial cost (cloud billing, paid APIs, paid tiers) without explicitly asking the user first. This includes:

- Cloud service billing modes (on-demand, reserved, spot)
- Paid API tiers or usage-based pricing
- Resource provisioning that incurs charges

Always present the cost implications and wait for explicit approval before proceeding.
